OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRemaining windy on Thursday
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers, however
OL,7,Fthese merging at times to give longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain, and possible the odd
OL,9,Frumble of thunder. Near normal
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,13,Fless frequent on Friday. A spell of
OL,14,Frain and stronger winds arriving
OL,15,FSaturday, with showers or longer
OL,16,Fspells of rain on Sunday. Temperatures
OL,17,Fclose to or slightly below normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
